Campaign:
Usually stores one-time or manually scheduled marketing campaigns (e.g., a Black Friday blast, a single promo email).

TriggerCampaign:
Designed for automated, rule-based, repeating campaigns. It stores extra logic: trigger rules, repeat delay, per-customer throttling, and expiration.







